data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Recent Price Improvement!! Can we say AFFORDABLE? Priced UNDER $305k, this RUSKIN Location Cannot be Beat! NO CDD, NO FLOOD ZONE and EXTREMELY LOW HOA! The HOA Fees for the Gorgeous Community Pool, Fitness Center, Clubhouse, Basketball Courts, & Playground are only $178.00 Quarterly! This newer 3 BD/2 BA Ruskin home is a STEAL and so well-kept! No worries about having to replace or repair a ROOR, AC or WATER HEATER - because this adorable home was built in 2014! Storm-Rated Windows, BRAND NEW TILE in Entry, Living Room and Guest Bath. Split floorplan with spacious Owners Suite featuring ceiling fans, carpet in great condition and a large walk-in closet with an AMAZING CUSTOM CLOSET ORGANIZATION system, that you have to see to believe. Owner's Bath has a glassed in shower, one vanity/sink, and neutral formica counters with lineleoum floors. Two more spacious bedrooms are across the home with a bathroom situated between. Each bedroom has carpet in excellent condition, ceiling fans, and large closets. The Guest Bath has the brand-new tile that matches the LR/FOYER and one vanity/sink and a tub/shower combo. The guest bath is located between the two Guest Bedrooms, but it is not a Jack and Jill. The spacious kitchen has cabinets galore, with an eat-in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, sizeable closet pantry and a breakfast bar. There are two patios on the home (front and back) that are unscreened and the backyard is completely fenced with luxury vinyl to contain your furry friends. Electric laundry hookups are in the garage; washer/dryer/outdoor freezer/garage shelving do NOT convey. You will find the home is priced under neighborhood comps. Owners are first reponders and are only moving because they are expanding their family and need more space! Easy access to MacDill AFB and Ruskin is a hot spot for PD, EMS, & Military due to the close proximity to I-75, Base, & Medical Facilities. 15-20 minutes away from downtown Tampa and the Airport, and Brandon/Riverview are twin cities that have every restaurant, shopping or medical facility that you will ever need - plus a Costco, Sam's and Mall. Don't miss this one - as it's priced to sell and homes don't last long in this incredible neighborhood. A fast closing date is important to the Sellers(s). Book your showing and Bring Your Offers before this one is SOLD!
